event.title: FSFE-booth at national NLLGG-meeting in Utrecht, Netherlands

body.p: On September 21, 2024, from about 10 to 16 o'clock we will be available with a FSFE-booth at the national NLLGG-meeting, Gerrit Rietveld College, Eykmanlaan 1200, 3571 KH Utrecht, the Netherlands. We are looking forward to have a chat with you about Free Software!
